B.t2=new A.bj(B.ti,["A CAT'S DAY","A comic-style trainer for future cat owners","PLAY","Settings","Cat care guide","Settings","Sound effects","Background music",'"Kitten on the Keys" \xb7 "The Entertainer" (ragtime, public domain)',"\u042f\u0437\u044b\u043a / Language","Back","Cat care guide","Your day with Misty and kitten Biscuit lasts 10 minutes \u2014 morning to night.\n\n\u2022 BOWL: cats eat 2\u20133 times a day. See a food bubble \u2014 tap the bowls to feed.\n\u2022 LITTER BOX: clean it after use. Cats refuse a dirty box and will yell about it.\n\u2022 PLAY: kittens need frequent play, adults at least twice a day. Tap the toy basket.\n\u2022 CLAWS: scratching is natural! If a cat attacks the sofa or wallpaper, stop it with a tap and offer the scratching post.\n\u2022 TABLE: cats love pushing things off. Be quick!\n\u2022 AFFECTION: pet the cats \u2014 tap a cat when it asks for attention.\n\u2022 BIRDS: bird-watching is cat TV. Let them enjoy it!\n\nComplete tasks in time or the cats will start YELLING. Good luck!","Paused","Resume","Restart","Main menu","Score","Time","Tasks","Feed the cats","Clean the litter box","Play with the cats","Pet","Stop the mischief!","Doorbell \u2014 open the door!","Fetch the mouse from under the sofa","Tip: a scratching post saves your furniture. Everybody wins!","Tip: feed cats on a schedule, 2\u20133 times a day.","Tip: a dirty litter box is the #1 cause of accidents.","Tip: 15 minutes of play a day keeps boredom-mischief away.","Tip: cats need affection too. But only when THEY want it.",'A box! Cat logic: "If I fits \u2014 I sits."',"Bird-watching is cat TV. Great for their minds!","Nobody at the door.","Pick up shards right away \u2014 cats can get hurt!","Evening zoomies are normal! Cats burn off energy.","Cats sleep 12\u201316 hours a day. Never wake them \u2014 it is sacred.","Thunderstorm! Cats fear thunder \u2014 let them hide, it is normal.","A fly got in! The best free cat exercise machine.","Cats love knocking pots off. Keep plants away from edges \u2014 and check they are not toxic to cats!","A puddle?! The cat refused the dirty litter box. Clean it in time!","CRASH!","MEOW!","MEE-OW-W!!!","purrr\u2026","scritch-scratch","DING!","KA-BOOM!","OOPS\u2026","NO!","zzz\u2026","Misty","Biscuit","Morning","Day","Evening","Night","DAY SURVIVED!","THE CATS ARE NOT AMUSED\u2026","Tasks completed","Failed","Things ruined","What you learned:","Feed on schedule","Keep the litter box clean","Play every day","Redirect claws to the post","Respect cat rituals","Play again","Purr-fect cat owner! 3 stars!","Great! The cats are mostly pleased.","Not bad, but there is room to grow.","The cats are on strike. Try again!","Morning! Misty and Biscuit are already awake.\nTap objects and cats to take care of them.\nSurvive the day \u2014 10 minutes!","Start the day","Mood","How to play:","\ud83c\udf57 Bowls (left) \u2014 feed","\ud83e\uddf9 Litter box (by the door) \u2014 clean","\ud83e\uddf6 Toy basket \u2014 play","\ud83d\udc3e A cat \u2014 pet it or stop mischief","\ud83d\udc46 Or tap a task card \u2014 the owner does it himself","tap the bowls","tap the litter box","tap the toy basket","tap the cat","tap the naughty cat!","tap the door","tap the sofa"],t.li)
